936
00:56:40,400 --> 00:56:41,640
<i>To ma akože nevidíš?</i>

937
00:56:43,620 --> 00:56:46,770
<i>Hae Yoonina mama...
Prečo si to urobila?</i>

938
00:56:47,630 --> 00:56:48,740
<i>Ty hajzel!</i>

939
00:56:51,160 --> 00:56:52,640
<i>Ty bastard!</i>

940
00:56:54,600 --> 00:56:55,710
<i>Han Chae Young?</i>

941
00:56:56,690 --> 00:56:58,110
<i>Gong Ki Joong?</i>

942
00:56:58,830 --> 00:57:00,150
<i>Tu, prosím.</i>

943
00:57:00,150 --> 00:57:01,840
<i>Uvedom sa!</i>

944
00:57:01,840 --> 00:57:06,470
<i>Majú z nás srandu, keď sa neukážu
na čas, keď sa máme stretnúť?</i>

945
00:57:08,560 --> 00:57:11,260
<i>Museli sme sa zmieriť
s absurdnou situáciou!</i>

946
00:57:13,140 --> 00:57:15,630
<i>Rozíďme sa, Hae Yoon.</i>

